---
title: Honey-Garlic Pork & Roast Veggie Salad with Feta & Toasted Pumpkin Seeds
description: The combination of garlic and honey infuses this colourful meal for a flavoursome result that comes together with minimal effort. Top it off with toasted pumpkin seeds and feta for a 5-star finish.
